SUB_W07_EVAR_DIVA_MISSION_141_CUT_000_02.text:
Ah, you must be the Soul Voyager.
The temple told us you'd be coming;
we are excited to behold your success.

SUB_W07_EVAR_DIVA_MISSION_233_CUT_000_04.text:
Oh, but I've no desire to destroy your port;
why would I want to be doing that, even?
I think I know why ye are confused here.

SUB_W07_FUNC_DIVA_MISSIONCONFIRMATION_TE.text:
